  m_Name: Level_03_Aguateca
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  levelNumber: 3
  levelName: Aguateca
  location: Peten, Guatemala
  levelDescription: "Here, the fire of war met the ink of wisdom.\n\nHigh on a cliff
    above the Petexbat\xFAn Lagoon, Aguateca stood as a fortified stronghold in the
    Late Classic period.\nIts rulers commanded both warriors and scribes, leaving
    behind walls etched with royal pride.\n\nThe city fell suddenly \u2014 attacked
    and abandoned in haste.\nObjects were left where they lay: tools, pigments, and
    codex fragments, frozen in time.\n\nExcavations reveal a city that valued knowledge
    as much as power, a rare glimpse into daily elite life."
